				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Goblin Gazughi Ring vs. Tiny Cloak of Darkest Night<a name="55387"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Aug 6 04 6:44 AM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>So, now I arrive at my dilemma.  Last night I was helping a guildie on a corpse run in LoLO and happened upon a Sarnak courier, I dropped him and he dropped the Goblin Gazughi Ring.  Now my question is, to do the Tiny Cloak of Darkest Night Caller cycle or is the Goblin Gazughi Ring that much better?  I my mind there are pluses to both:
<br />

<br />
<b>Goblin Gazughi Ring</b>
<br />
Instance Clicky
<br />

<br />
<b>Tiny Cloak of Darkest Night</b>
<br />
1.5 sec cast
<br />
Ammo slot
<br />
Self targeting
<br />
Has uses beyond swarm kiting
<br />

<br />
To me, I can sell the Goblin Gazughi Ring and be better off.  I have been swarming with just the Invis song and doing farely well.  To me the Tiny Cloak of Darkest Night fits better into my swarm kiting modus operandi.  Thoughts?
<br />

<br />
</span></td>
