				<td colspan="2"><span>I agree with Wound.  I've got both, and I use them for COMPLETELY different situations.  When I find the occasion to charm or swarm kite, the Goblin ring is FAR superior to the tiny cloak (becasue of insta-clicky timing on breaking charm).
<br />

<br />
Now, that being said, there is an item that you can consider an upgrade to the ring, and that is Boots of the Mosquito.  With the boots, you don't have to target yourself to cast the invis vs animals.  With the Goblin ring you do have to.
<br />

<br />
Keep the ring (for charm/swarm kiting) until you get Boots of Mosquito.  Keep the Tiny Cloak forever.
<br />

<br />
</span></td>
