				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: Goblin Gazughi Ring vs. Tiny Cloak of Darkest Night<a name="55398"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Aug 6 04 8:58 AM</span></td>
